reviewText: This dvd is just a bunch of porn stars & nude models getting interviewed at an Adult Con.  Everyone stays clothed.  Interviews are all under a couple of minutes each.  Some hold up their 2007 projects, others prance about in their benefactor's clothing like Hustler.  Do NOT buy this unless you want to watch these women talk for a minute about meeting fans & the like.  I would give it 0 stars, but I cant.
